name: Sai-Ani_Kannu
content:
Sai-Ani Kannu was a male Cerean who worked as an assassin and a bounty hunter during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.
During the Clone Wars, Kannu met with a Human in the bar Crater's on the planet Cularin, and the man hired Kannu to protect eleven individuals in the Cularin system who had contracts against their lives.
